 Department, located in the main hospital lobby.</p>\n<!-- /epsilon/About-->\n<!-- /epsilon/about -->\n \n<!-- epsilon/specialties -->\nCovid-19 Questionnaire\nNous valorisons nos patients\n[contact-form-7 id=\"6\" title=\"Formulaire\"]\n<!-- epsilon/Specialties -->\nNeurology\nOutside of a medical emergency, your primary care physician is the \"first responder\" to your healthcare needs\n<!-- /epsilon/Specialties-->\n<!-- epsilon/Specialties -->\nSurgery\nState-of-the-art surgical facilities where expert surgeons perform a full complement of procedures.\n<!-- /epsilon/Specialties-->\n<!-- epsilon/Specialties -->\nCardio\nFew of us like to even think about having a heart attack or being with someone when they have one.\n<!-- /epsilon/Specialties-->\n<!-- epsilon/Specialties -->\nOncology\nRehabilitation services for conditions ranging from stroke and brain injury to neurological disorders.\n<!-- /epsilon/Specialties-->\n<!-- /epsilon/specialties -->\n \n<!-- epsilon/openhours -->\nStatistique\n[cov2019map]\n<p class=\"text-center\">[mmscovidlive country=\"Tunisia\" title=\"Global\" style=\"4\" label_confirmed=\"Confirmed\" label_deaths=\"Deaths\" label_recovered=\"Recovered\"]</p>\n<img src=\"http://localhost/Corona-19/wp-content/themes/medzone-lite/assets/images/03_top_experience.png\" />\n<!-- epsilon/Schedule -->\nMonday - Thursday\n9:30 am - 8:30 pm\n<!-- /epsilon/Schedule-->\n<!-- epsilon/Schedule -->\nFriday\n9:30 am - 8:30 pm\n<!-- /epsilon/Schedule-->\n<!-- epsilon/Schedule -->\nWeekend\n10:30 am - 5:30 pm\n<!-- /epsilon/Schedule-->\n<!-- epsilon/Schedule -->\nHoliday\n<a href=\'#\'>Check Dates <i class=\'fa fa-angle-down\'></i></a>\n<!-- /epsilon/Schedule-->\n<!-- /epsilon/openhours -->\n \n<!-- epsilon/doctors -->\nMeet our Doctors\n<p class=\"text-center\">Our experts are here for you every single day! We care about our patients and we<br>do our best to make them happy.</p>\n<!-- epsilon/Doctors -->\nDr. House Greg\nGodlike\n<p>Pellentesque dapibus tristi